Ecological notes : very common in broad-leaved, mixed and carr woodland; partly wooded heathland; wetlands including fen, water meadows and basin mire with
Menyanthes
bog; gravel pits; ditch along meadow hedge; old hedges; disused railway cutting; garden; common on unimproved calcareous grassland. iv–viii, x.
